To create django project
1. run virtual environment: python3 -m venv vene <virtual_environment_name>
2. activate the virtual environment: source ~/venv/src/bin/activate
3. install django project: django-admin startproject <project-name>
4. to access python shell: python3 manage.py shell
5. to run the django project: python3 manage.py runserver
6. pip3 install -r requirements.txt
#python-dotenv is used to set up configuration variables
7. to install a .env file: use pip3 install python-dotenv
8. to install django rest framework: pip3 install djangorestframework
9. to install python unit testing framework - pip3 install pytest
10. for django testing: pip3 install pytest-django